Overview

This dashboard shows GlobalProtect and HIPMatch overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested GlobalProtect and HIPMatch logs from Prisma Access.

It includes HIP Match Events by OS, Top Host Name, GlobalProtect Events by Authentication Method, Top Error Message for Unsuccessful Connection, GlobalProtect Events by Gateway Selection Method, GlobalProtect Events by Gateway Location, Top Quarantine Reason, and Average SSL Response Time. These visualizations provide critical insights into endpoint security, remote access management, and network performance.
